The paper deals with generating special effects for typography, which involves image processing and computer vision techniques. Therefore, cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely categories. The paper also involves statistical analysis and machine learning techniques, which are covered by cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the use of soft constraints, which is a topic covered by cs.LG (Machine Learning).
